# GymBro API — Documentation System

Before any backend task, read the relevant shared docs in `../docs/`:

| What you need | Read |
|---|---|
| Project structure, layers | `../docs/architecture.md` |
| Domain entities, EF filters | `../docs/domain-model.md` |
| API surface (major endpoints) | `../docs/backend-api.md` |
| Auth, JWT, ICurrentUser | `../docs/architecture.md` |
