## Key conventions

- All handlers return `Result<T>` — never throw
- Controllers only map Result → HTTP status codes
- EF global filters: tenant isolation + soft-delete (admin bypasses both)
- `X-Tenant-Id` header required for all tenant-scoped API calls
- FluentValidation validators live beside their command files
- Namespaces: `Modules.<ModuleName>.<Layer>.<Subfolder>`
- DTO mapping: explicit only in `Application/Mapping/<Module>Mapping.cs` (see repo root `CLAUDE.md`)

## Update rules (MANDATORY)

After every code change, update the corresponding doc:

- New endpoint → `../docs/backend-api.md`
- New entity field → `../docs/domain-model.md`
- New permission check → `../docs/permissions-and-roles.md`
- Invite / bootstrap change → `../docs/business-flows.md`
- Tenant isolation change → `../docs/architecture.md`
